Subject autoquest store~
Text
There should be a black market store in kowloon that you can sell autoquest
equipment for quest points. You only get 50% of what you paid for it and it
should sell previously enjoyed equipment for %50 more than what it was bought
for. For example, someone buys a sash from the questmaster for 4000qp, they
sell it on the black market for 2000qp, someone decides to buy it, it costs
3000qp for them. This way, if immortals plan on making more quest equipment
as prizes for quests, it should be marked as autoquest equipment so that it
has some sort of value on the black market, this way no one gets ripped off
and rich people always have a way to get something out of the quest equipment
they don't need anymore and getting something in return rather than dealing
with other rich people and lots of poor people. I don't know if this system
can be implemented but it would be nice.

If you ask why bother? Well, autoquest equipment will always have level
restrictment. So rather than buying a new one, you can see if the black market
man has something to sell for you!
~
