Subject Cleric Heal Spell~
Text
This is an idea to counter monks' amazingly high healing capabilities.
Since CLERICS are supposed to be all holy and healing and stuff...
Maybe their healing spells sould be based on current mana or mvs as well.
The reasoning behind this is because if they are up against
a rapidstriking warrior, circling thief, dragonpunching monk, or ra tilting mage
their hp drops drastically.
Right now, I use heal outside of battle after fleeing/teleporting because if I cast it in mid-battle, I get overwhelmed

If it was a bit more potent for non-Espers, it would be a little more useful, unless you guys just go "just make 3x heals".
I dunno, I'm just thinking like a dork again.

